{"tid":2309376,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"刺針之死早有徵兆 被裁記者：努力工作俾人一手摧毀 許方輝「空降」唯獨對刺針組同事不聞不問","createTime":"2020-12-02T13:26:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T18:06:54.000Z","uid":240362,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9c399d99daa1cb7510de88bd002177aea7050900","tid":2309376,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:26:57.000Z","msg":"有線新聞以偵查報道著稱的專題組《新聞刺針》全數3名記者被裁，外界質疑是出於政治考慮。有被裁的記者稱，部份同事仍有即將「埋尾」的新聞故事在手，惟已沒有機會完成；有早前已離職的《刺針》記者形容，《刺針》並非「突然死亡」，而是早有徵兆。<br />\n<br />\n記者關玉婷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/iIGHlzQ-2E2Zhql2-s0oBmcmUw4=/802x464/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OT6IYZQ4VJGXHDPOI447OZNB5M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FiIGHlzQ-2E2Zhql2-s0oBmcmUw4%3D%2F802x464%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOT6IYZQ4VJGXHDPOI447OZNB5M.jpg&h=a82fd483&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n丘庭亮說：「前一日大家仲喺度努力工作，下一日已經俾人一手摧毀咗。」資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n丘庭亮今年剛從大學畢業，在《刺針》全職工作只有不足半年，月薪13,000多元，卻也成為裁員名單上的一員。昨日早上11時許，他和同組的另外兩名同事陸續接到沒有來電顯示的電話，被叫入會議室。「大家聽HR（人事部）講條款、賠償，跟住簽名。」他稱，房內除了被裁的員工，就只有人事部職員和保安，4名高層未有現身。「前一日大家仲喺度努力工作，下一日已經俾人一手摧毀咗。」<br />\n<br />\n對報道臨別前順利「出街」感幸運<br />\n<br />\n他稱自讀書時已經嚮往在《刺針》工作，過往工作也不曾遇過新聞審查：「唔會特別有條紅線乜嘢唔做得，或者一定要做乜嘢。大家討論嘅角度，唔會係敏唔敏感。」該組上星期刊出的報道，探討建制陣營引用民意調查的代表性，便是出自他手筆。他稱臨別前報道能順利「出街」，自己屬於較幸運的一員：「有同事隻故仔（新聞故事）已經做到埋緊尾，差唔多咩都拍晒！」那隻花費不少心血的新聞故事，最終可能無緣與觀眾見面。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201202/J757V2FRUFAP5FELDAFC6HBMRA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201202%2FJ757V2FRUFAP5FELDAFC6HBMRA%2F&d=u42ujRIT%2FE%2FeodHrCKN%2BObScfX6drAaaDYLMstvIIS4%3D&h=2d964b9f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201202%2FJ757V2FRUFAP5FELDAFC6HBMRA%2F&h=a3cce3da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201202/J757V2FRUFAP5FELDAFC6HBMRA/</a>"},{"pid":"d53f56014543f941597aec6751823def3a1165aa","tid":2309376,"uid":86233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:29:22.000Z","msg":"等睇有線執笠"},{"pid":"aa0b5066048c41f1f932b2139126fc1daad12f2d","tid":2309376,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:29:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25091fc29a5b38d5a79422ad7eea05298b5bd3fb","tid":2309376,"uid":105605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:29:58.000Z","msg":"萬3..."},{"pid":"cd9ac59ba3b2780b2e296b115aa2a5c17449d9d4","tid":2309376,"uid":222614,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:43:50.000Z","msg":"香港人僅餘嘅偵查能力都無埋 ...."},{"pid":"96a3e12461247b6ecabc9e93afab1df1cc88edd5","tid":2309376,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:45:53.000Z","msg":"刺針唔執，記者人生安全會受威脅 ...."},{"pid":"a5582cc86a3ac78511e19bc896a531bdaca1ca85","tid":2309376,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:47:30.000Z","msg":"pushh"},{"pid":"7e9d95e3e079ec88e0030a1f5e9dfcb2e187bebf","tid":2309376,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T14:02:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24eb9cceacf06b77d8a5ed04bf74103daebe26d3","tid":2309376,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T14:49:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd080e50e3f51059ce5ef3cb7632be32f43ed38b","t